Dialogue: 99,0:00:00.89,0:00:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,♪
Dialogue: 99,0:00:09.90,0:00:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[wind blowing]
Dialogue: 99,0:00:14.70,0:00:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- [creaking]\N- [Coco gasps softly]
Dialogue: 99,0:00:19.83,0:00:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the wind?
Dialogue: 99,0:00:24.29,0:00:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- [QIFREY] Ah, you're awake.\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 99,0:00:26.71,0:00:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[Qifrey grunts softly]
Dialogue: 99,0:00:28.04,0:00:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I took the liberty of hailing us\Na Pegasus Carriage.
Dialogue: 99,0:00:30.63,0:00:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO] Huh?
Dialogue: 99,0:00:31.92,0:00:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be chilly,
Dialogue: 99,0:00:33.13,0:00:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,flying so high\Nin your bedclothes.
Dialogue: 99,0:00:35.55,0:00:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Our ride's almost over.
Dialogue: 99,0:00:38.72,0:00:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh, look there.\N- [Coco gasps]
Dialogue: 99,0:00:40.77,0:00:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Our destination.
Dialogue: 99,0:00:42.39,0:00:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco gasps]
Dialogue: 99,0:00:44.27,0:00:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 99,0:00:46.48,0:00:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,♪
Dialogue: 99,0:00:51.94,0:00:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[QIFREY] That is my atelier.
Dialogue: 99,0:00:54.20,0:00:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And your new place of study.
Dialogue: 99,0:00:58.28,0:01:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[♪ opening theme song playing]
Dialogue: 99,0:02:31.50,0:02:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[QIFREY] Don't worry\Nabout your house.
Dialogue: 99,0:02:33.50,0:02:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I planted Guard Briar seeds\Nall around it.
Dialogue: 99,0:02:36.55,0:02:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll grow quickly,\Nand as they do,
Dialogue: 99,0:02:38.76,0:02:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,they'll form\Na protective barrier.
Dialogue: 99,0:02:40.97,0:02:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The spell that petrified\Nyour house,
Dialogue: 99,0:02:43.35,0:02:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,is presently unknown to us.
Dialogue: 99,0:02:45.35,0:02:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Best to keep\Nany careless visitors
Dialogue: 99,0:02:47.23,0:02:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,from getting too close.
Dialogue: 99,0:02:53.90,0:02:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 99,0:02:55.40,0:02:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh?
Dialogue: 99,0:02:57.28,0:02:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Coco?
Dialogue: 99,0:03:03.57,0:03:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 99,0:03:05.16,0:03:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[crying]\NI promised my mother
Dialogue: 99,0:03:07.08,0:03:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that I would never leave her\Nall alone,
Dialogue: 99,0:03:10.42,0:03:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and now, I...
Dialogue: 99,0:03:12.38,0:03:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 99,0:03:18.17,0:03:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't blame yourself.
Dialogue: 99,0:03:20.93,0:03:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't know.
Dialogue: 99,0:03:26.31,0:03:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[door closes]
Dialogue: 99,0:03:29.56,0:03:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[footsteps]
Dialogue: 99,0:03:31.48,0:03:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,♪
Dialogue: 99,0:03:35.11,0:03:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[QIFREY] Here,\Nto wash your face.
Dialogue: 99,0:03:37.90,0:03:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let your tears fall behind you,\Nand look forward.
Dialogue: 99,0:03:43.53,0:03:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,As of today,\Nthis shall be your home.
Dialogue: 99,0:03:47.74,0:03:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco gasps]
Dialogue: 99,0:03:53.75,0:03:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO] Uh...
Dialogue: 99,0:03:56.84,0:04:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- [COCO] Um, what is this?\N- [QIFREY] Hm?
Dialogue: 99,0:04:00.21,0:04:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, it's water.
Dialogue: 99,0:04:01.63,0:04:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 99,0:04:03.51,0:04:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I forget?\NYou'll need a change of clothes.
Dialogue: 99,0:04:05.93,0:04:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO] Water isn't usually\Nso round and floaty.
Dialogue: 99,0:04:07.85,0:04:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'll be back in a flash.\N- [gasps]
Dialogue: 99,0:04:09.56,0:04:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, could you explain
Dialogue: 99,0:04:11.56,0:04:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,how I'm supposed\Nto use this first?
Dialogue: 99,0:04:14.27,0:04:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Qifrey?
Dialogue: 99,0:04:18.15,0:04:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Touching magic\NI know nothing about
Dialogue: 99,0:04:20.23,0:04:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,is a little scary now.
Dialogue: 99,0:04:21.78,0:04:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[GIRL] Aw, don't be scared!
Dialogue: 99,0:04:24.11,0:04:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Far as spells go,\Nthat one's pretty simple.
Dialogue: 99,0:04:27.12,0:04:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 99,0:04:29.24,0:04:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell you all about it\Nif you want me to!
Dialogue: 99,0:04:33.79,0:04:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco gasps softly]
Dialogue: 99,0:04:34.96,0:04:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What you've got there\Nis a Vapor Bubble.
Dialogue: 99,0:04:37.42,0:04:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a kind of magic that takes\Nmoisture out of the air
Dialogue: 99,0:04:40.25,0:04:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and turns it into water.
Dialogue: 99,0:04:41.63,0:04:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold out your hands for me.
Dialogue: 99,0:04:43.17,0:04:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Here! Go on!
Dialogue: 99,0:04:45.59,0:04:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You tilt the lower tray\Nlike this,
Dialogue: 99,0:04:47.76,0:04:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and the water comes flowing out!
Dialogue: 99,0:04:49.64,0:04:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, amazing.\NThanks so much.
Dialogue: 99,0:04:53.35,0:04:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thank you!\N- [COCO] Huh?
Dialogue: 99,0:04:55.52,0:04:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I always love it so when\Npeople tell me "thank you."
Dialogue: 99,0:04:58.65,0:05:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So thank you for your thanks!
Dialogue: 99,0:05:00.65,0:05:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO] Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 99,0:05:02.78,0:05:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you, again.
Dialogue: 99,0:05:05.78,0:05:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And thank you!
Dialogue: 99,0:05:06.99,0:05:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That one's\Nfor thanking me again!
Dialogue: 99,0:05:08.66,0:05:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you too!\NThank you for thanking me
Dialogue: 99,0:05:11.29,0:05:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- for thanking you.\N- [GIRL 2] Stop responding,
Dialogue: 99,0:05:13.20,0:05:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- just ignore her.\N- [both gasp]
Dialogue: 99,0:05:16.29,0:05:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll tire herself out\Nand give up.
Dialogue: 99,0:05:19.29,0:05:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Richeh, you're so mean!
Dialogue: 99,0:05:21.30,0:05:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I was actually being\Nvery helpful,
Dialogue: 99,0:05:23.34,0:05:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have you know.
Dialogue: 99,0:05:24.72,0:05:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco gasps]
Dialogue: 99,0:05:26.01,0:05:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO] The pen and ink.
Dialogue: 99,0:05:28.89,0:05:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Would the two of you\Nhappen to be witches?
Dialogue: 99,0:05:31.72,0:05:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We're apprentices.
Dialogue: 99,0:05:33.31,0:05:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Students studying\Nwith Master Qifrey.
Dialogue: 99,0:05:35.69,0:05:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, if you're asking,\Nthen are you not?
Dialogue: 99,0:05:38.23,0:05:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So what are you?
Dialogue: 99,0:05:39.44,0:05:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the same age\Nas Richeh and I?
Dialogue: 99,0:05:41.48,0:05:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you? Looks like it.
Dialogue: 99,0:05:43.19,0:05:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And what atelier\Ndid you come here from?
Dialogue: 99,0:05:45.32,0:05:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco exhales nervously]
Dialogue: 99,0:05:46.65,0:05:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, uh, I think\Nit's still a little early
Dialogue: 99,0:05:49.16,0:05:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,to call myself a student.
Dialogue: 99,0:05:50.62,0:05:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, before yesterday,
Dialogue: 99,0:05:52.41,0:05:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I had never drawn\Na spell in my life.
Dialogue: 99,0:05:55.04,0:05:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But I do live here\Nstarting today.
Dialogue: 99,0:05:58.75,0:06:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH] Oh...
Dialogue: 99,0:06:01.04,0:06:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 99,0:06:02.46,0:06:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's you.
Dialogue: 99,0:06:03.88,0:06:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one\Nthat rumor's about?
Dialogue: 99,0:06:05.67,0:06:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?\NWhat rumor?
Dialogue: 99,0:06:08.93,0:06:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[exclaims softly]
Dialogue: 99,0:06:10.55,0:06:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,♪
Dialogue: 99,0:06:16.06,0:06:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[GIRL] People have been\Ntalking about an Outsider
Dialogue: 99,0:06:19.94,0:06:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,who made use of forbidden magic,
Dialogue: 99,0:06:22.44,0:06:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and was then allowed\Nto become an apprentice
Dialogue: 99,0:06:25.23,0:06:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,with her memories intact.
Dialogue: 99,0:06:28.07,0:06:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- [QIFREY] Coco?\N- [Coco gasps]
Dialogue: 99,0:06:31.07,0:06:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 99,0:06:32.45,0:06:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 99,0:06:33.83,0:06:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks as though you've all been\Ngetting acquainted
Dialogue: 99,0:06:36.12,0:06:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,with each other.
Dialogue: 99,0:06:37.29,0:06:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Richeh, Tetia,\Nonce you're finished helping
Dialogue: 99,0:06:39.54,0:06:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,with the morning chores,\Nwill you go study in your rooms?
Dialogue: 99,0:06:42.08,0:06:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- All right!\N- Hm.
Dialogue: 99,0:06:44.46,0:06:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[QIFREY] Here. It's what\Nall my students wear.
Dialogue: 99,0:06:47.51,0:06:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco exclaims softly]
Dialogue: 99,0:06:50.01,0:06:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't worry.
Dialogue: 99,0:06:51.76,0:06:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I will explain everything.
Dialogue: 99,0:06:54.14,0:06:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[birds chirping]
Dialogue: 99,0:06:56.14,0:06:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[QIFREY]\NLooks like a perfect fit.
Dialogue: 99,0:06:58.64,0:06:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco exhales softly]
Dialogue: 99,0:07:00.44,0:07:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, I shall share with you\Nthe history of magic.
Dialogue: 99,0:07:03.90,0:07:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco gasps softly] Hm.
Dialogue: 99,0:07:07.49,0:07:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[QIFREY] Long ago...
Dialogue: 99,0:07:09.15,0:07:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,magic was a part\Nof ordinary life.
Dialogue: 99,0:07:11.66,0:07:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[scribbling]
Dialogue: 99,0:07:13.28,0:07:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All that one needed to use it
Dialogue: 99,0:07:15.28,0:07:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,was a special ink\Nand a set of patterns.
Dialogue: 99,0:07:19.29,0:07:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,♪
Dialogue: 99,0:07:23.58,0:07:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[QIFREY] It was a simple,\Nfamiliar tool,
Dialogue: 99,0:07:25.80,0:07:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,available to anyone\Nand everyone.
Dialogue: 99,0:07:30.13,0:07:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet at the same time,
Dialogue: 99,0:07:32.01,0:07:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,it was a constant source\Nof conflict.
Dialogue: 99,0:07:34.72,0:07:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[faint clamoring]
Dialogue: 99,0:07:36.51,0:07:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[QIFREY] When mankind holds\Nthe power to do anything,
Dialogue: 99,0:07:39.89,0:07:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,"anything" is what they do.
Dialogue: 99,0:07:41.69,0:07:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Many horrific spells\Nwere created.
Dialogue: 99,0:07:48.82,0:07:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The few good souls\Nwho remained in the world
Dialogue: 99,0:07:51.53,0:07:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,renounced war and strife,
Dialogue: 99,0:07:53.61,0:07:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and banded together\Nas witches.
Dialogue: 99,0:07:55.95,0:07:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They stole away\Nhumanity's memory of magic,
Dialogue: 99,0:07:58.87,0:08:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,letting it only be known\Nto their disciples,
Dialogue: 99,0:08:01.00,0:08:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,who were sworn to protect it.
Dialogue: 99,0:08:04.17,0:08:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the Day of the Pact.
Dialogue: 99,0:08:07.00,0:08:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Since then,\Npeople have believed
Dialogue: 99,0:08:08.63,0:08:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that magic is a power\Nonly a chosen few can wield.
Dialogue: 99,0:08:12.17,0:08:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If the truth came to light,
Dialogue: 99,0:08:14.01,0:08:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the world would fall\Ninto chaos once again.
Dialogue: 99,0:08:17.81,0:08:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, that's why\Nwe've taken such care
Dialogue: 99,0:08:20.18,0:08:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,to preserve the secret.
Dialogue: 99,0:08:21.56,0:08:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And why your story\Nhas traveled so quickly.
Dialogue: 99,0:08:24.52,0:08:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 99,0:08:25.77,0:08:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 99,0:08:26.94,0:08:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I've brought\Nall this upon myself.
Dialogue: 99,0:08:29.48,0:08:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 99,0:08:31.24,0:08:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What is "forbidden magic"?
Dialogue: 99,0:08:34.49,0:08:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic drawn\Nduring the age of war,
Dialogue: 99,0:08:36.82,0:08:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and banished upon\Nthe Day of the Pact.
Dialogue: 99,0:08:40.20,0:08:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic for hurting people.
Dialogue: 99,0:08:42.16,0:08:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco gasps]
Dialogue: 99,0:08:44.67,0:08:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO] Teach me, I beg you!
Dialogue: 99,0:08:46.67,0:08:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me learn about\Nthis Forbidden Magic!
Dialogue: 99,0:08:48.84,0:08:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to understand it!
Dialogue: 99,0:08:51.71,0:08:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go on not knowing.
Dialogue: 99,0:08:54.09,0:08:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too frightening to bear!
Dialogue: 99,0:08:57.09,0:09:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, I tell my students\Nnot to rush themselves,
Dialogue: 99,0:09:00.56,0:09:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,but I fear\Nit's too late for that.
Dialogue: 99,0:09:05.27,0:09:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 99,0:09:11.40,0:09:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There are any number\Nof forbidden spells
Dialogue: 99,0:09:13.57,0:09:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I could list.\NBut to keep it simple,
Dialogue: 99,0:09:16.36,0:09:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,it's like so...
Dialogue: 99,0:09:18.53,0:09:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Any spell cast directly\Nupon the human body
Dialogue: 99,0:09:21.24,0:09:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,is utterly prohibited.
Dialogue: 99,0:09:23.45,0:09:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This includes transformation,\Nage alteration,
Dialogue: 99,0:09:26.87,0:09:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,teleportation without the use\Nof doors or conveyances.
Dialogue: 99,0:09:30.29,0:09:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Manipulating thoughts\Nor emotions,
Dialogue: 99,0:09:32.80,0:09:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,doing harm to a person,\Nor healing them.
Dialogue: 99,0:09:36.18,0:09:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There is but one exception.
Dialogue: 99,0:09:38.80,0:09:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Erasing people's memories?
Dialogue: 99,0:09:41.01,0:09:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[QIFREY] Precisely...
Dialogue: 99,0:09:42.72,0:09:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, most spells\Nare cast on tools.
Dialogue: 99,0:09:49.02,0:09:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Like carriages, or lamps.
Dialogue: 99,0:09:52.78,0:09:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] Wow.
Dialogue: 99,0:09:57.99,0:10:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Or even windows,\Nsuch as this one.
Dialogue: 99,0:10:21.05,0:10:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a lake!
Dialogue: 99,0:10:23.51,0:10:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But we were surrounded by hills\Njust a moment ago.
Dialogue: 99,0:10:26.89,0:10:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[QIFREY] This is a Windowway.
Dialogue: 99,0:10:28.94,0:10:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It links two round windows\Nbearing the same pattern.
Dialogue: 99,0:10:32.48,0:10:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you see that building\Nin the distance?
Dialogue: 99,0:10:35.69,0:10:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tower of Tomes.
Dialogue: 99,0:10:37.49,0:10:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time a book on magic\Nis written,
Dialogue: 99,0:10:39.53,0:10:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,a copy instantly appears there,
Dialogue: 99,0:10:41.49,0:10:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,to ensure the knowledge within\Nis never lost.
Dialogue: 99,0:10:43.91,0:10:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco gasps]
Dialogue: 99,0:10:44.91,0:10:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll have the picture book.
Dialogue: 99,0:10:46.79,0:10:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take me there!
Dialogue: 99,0:10:48.08,0:10:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll search nonstop\Ntill I find it!
Dialogue: 99,0:10:49.92,0:10:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Slow down.
Dialogue: 99,0:10:51.00,0:10:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[water gushing]
Dialogue: 99,0:10:52.96,0:10:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[rumbling]
Dialogue: 99,0:11:00.63,0:11:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Qifrey grunts]\N- [Coco exclaims]
Dialogue: 99,0:11:02.64,0:11:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco groans]
Dialogue: 99,0:11:05.68,0:11:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,♪
Dialogue: 99,0:11:07.56,0:11:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]\NThat's the Librarians' Trial.
Dialogue: 99,0:11:11.35,0:11:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tower of Tomes is guarded\Nby four librarians,
Dialogue: 99,0:11:14.27,0:11:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and only witches\Nwho overcome their trials
Dialogue: 99,0:11:16.48,0:11:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,are allowed to enter.
Dialogue: 99,0:11:18.53,0:11:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you wish to visit,\Nyou're going to have to study.
Dialogue: 99,0:11:22.82,0:11:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Coco...
Dialogue: 99,0:11:24.53,0:11:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hearing of your\Neagerness to learn
Dialogue: 99,0:11:26.99,0:11:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,truly filled me with happiness.
Dialogue: 99,0:11:29.87,0:11:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And the fear you feel\Nis natural.
Dialogue: 99,0:11:32.67,0:11:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 99,0:11:35.00,0:11:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the spells which have\Nnot been forbidden...
Dialogue: 99,0:11:42.43,0:11:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,are the ones that bring\Nhappiness to people's lives.
Dialogue: 99,0:11:46.51,0:11:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think
Dialogue: 99,0:11:47.97,0:11:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd rather learn about\Na gentler kind of magic?
Dialogue: 99,0:11:50.43,0:11:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Coco gasps]\N- [QIFREY] What do you say?
Dialogue: 99,0:11:52.56,0:11:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO] Huh?
Dialogue: 99,0:11:53.56,0:11:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you interested?
Dialogue: 99,0:11:55.77,0:11:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 99,0:11:56.98,0:11:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, Master Qifrey.
Dialogue: 99,0:11:59.78,0:12:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[bird cawing]
Dialogue: 99,0:12:02.99,0:12:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This will be your room.
Dialogue: 99,0:12:07.70,0:12:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently Agott's not around.
Dialogue: 99,0:12:09.95,0:12:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO] Who's Agott?
Dialogue: 99,0:12:11.33,0:12:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[QIFREY]\NShe's your new roommate.
Dialogue: 99,0:12:17.42,0:12:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco exclaims softly]
Dialogue: 99,0:12:19.09,0:12:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[QIFREY] There's one workspace,\Nwhich you'll share,
Dialogue: 99,0:12:21.76,0:12:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and two bedrooms.
Dialogue: 99,0:12:23.59,0:12:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco gasps]
Dialogue: 99,0:12:25.84,0:12:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[QIFREY] They're down the stairs\Nin the back.
Dialogue: 99,0:12:28.22,0:12:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, the doors do lock.
Dialogue: 99,0:12:31.06,0:12:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Get some rest if you like.
Dialogue: 99,0:12:33.27,0:12:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I had better be on my way.
Dialogue: 99,0:12:34.94,0:12:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me if you need anything.
Dialogue: 99,0:12:39.48,0:12:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[footsteps]
Dialogue: 99,0:12:47.37,0:12:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, this is Qifrey.
Dialogue: 99,0:12:49.74,0:12:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Coco's settling in nicely.
Dialogue: 99,0:12:51.37,0:12:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for approving\Nher apprenticeship.
Dialogue: 99,0:12:54.87,0:12:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 99,0:12:56.79,0:12:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 99,0:12:58.29,0:12:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing on the book yet.
Dialogue: 99,0:12:59.67,0:13:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She may need a bit of time\Nto get adjusted.
Dialogue: 99,0:13:03.17,0:13:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco exclaims]
Dialogue: 99,0:13:04.76,0:13:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO] So this is what\Na witch's room looks like.
Dialogue: 99,0:13:09.26,0:13:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[AGOTT]\NThat's my side of the desk.
Dialogue: 99,0:13:11.60,0:13:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco gasps]
Dialogue: 99,0:13:23.19,0:13:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the way. I'm landing.
Dialogue: 99,0:13:25.82,0:13:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 99,0:13:34.91,0:13:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[exclaims softly]
Dialogue: 99,0:13:37.92,0:13:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 99,0:13:39.38,0:13:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- Agott, right? I'm Coco...\N- I know.
Dialogue: 99,0:13:42.38,0:13:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The famous Outsider, right?
Dialogue: 99,0:13:45.17,0:13:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand you'll be\Njoining us as an apprentice.
Dialogue: 99,0:13:49.22,0:13:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 99,0:13:50.51,0:13:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to hear\Nabout your mother.
Dialogue: 99,0:13:52.68,0:13:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. That's very kind.
Dialogue: 99,0:13:54.68,0:13:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[AGOTT] Because of you...
Dialogue: 99,0:13:58.81,0:14:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,she'll never be flesh\Nand blood again, will she?
Dialogue: 99,0:14:01.69,0:14:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco inhales sharply]
Dialogue: 99,0:14:03.03,0:14:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason I'm here\Nis to save her, if I can.
Dialogue: 99,0:14:06.15,0:14:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,By becoming a witch...
Dialogue: 99,0:14:10.28,0:14:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what my life has been.
Dialogue: 99,0:14:12.16,0:14:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Drawing casting seals\Ntill my fingers turned black.
Dialogue: 99,0:14:15.16,0:14:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Working and working\Nto pass the tests,
Dialogue: 99,0:14:17.54,0:14:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,so that one day\NI could become an apprentice.
Dialogue: 99,0:14:20.83,0:14:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know\Nthe first thing about it.
Dialogue: 99,0:14:23.17,0:14:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way\Nan Outsider like you
Dialogue: 99,0:14:25.09,0:14:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,will ever be a witch.
Dialogue: 99,0:14:26.42,0:14:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,♪
Dialogue: 99,0:14:29.34,0:14:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't know.
Dialogue: 99,0:14:30.76,0:14:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have drawn spells!
Dialogue: 99,0:14:33.47,0:14:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to at least try!
Dialogue: 99,0:14:35.10,0:14:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, then prove yourself.
Dialogue: 99,0:14:37.31,0:14:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Your test starts tomorrow--
Dialogue: 99,0:14:38.73,0:14:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[TETIA] Agott! Coco!
Dialogue: 99,0:14:40.73,0:14:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Food time!
Dialogue: 99,0:14:43.15,0:14:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- Let's go!\N- [stomach growls]
Dialogue: 99,0:14:47.78,0:14:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO] Excuse me!
Dialogue: 99,0:14:50.57,0:14:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I could eat a Pegasus.
Dialogue: 99,0:14:52.62,0:14:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I could, too!
Dialogue: 99,0:14:53.78,0:14:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And this will be\NCoco's welcome party!
Dialogue: 99,0:14:56.04,0:14:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- Such fun!\N- Such food.
Dialogue: 99,0:14:58.50,0:15:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,♪
Dialogue: 99,0:15:06.17,0:15:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Normal meal. Ugh.
Dialogue: 99,0:15:08.47,0:15:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Master,\Nwhere's the welcome party?
Dialogue: 99,0:15:12.26,0:15:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No time to prepare.
Dialogue: 99,0:15:13.76,0:15:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just have it\Nsome other day.
Dialogue: 99,0:15:16.14,0:15:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Agott?
Dialogue: 99,0:15:17.18,0:15:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm eating in my room."
Dialogue: 99,0:15:19.23,0:15:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's her choice,
Dialogue: 99,0:15:20.60,0:15:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,but I do wish she'd join us\Nevery once in a while.
Dialogue: 99,0:15:23.27,0:15:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, we don't want it\Nto get cold, do we?
Dialogue: 99,0:15:26.19,0:15:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your day, Coco.
Dialogue: 99,0:15:27.61,0:15:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you bless\Nthe meal for us?
Dialogue: 99,0:15:29.32,0:15:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO] Oh! Um...
Dialogue: 99,0:15:31.91,0:15:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We're grateful for this food.
Dialogue: 99,0:15:33.82,0:15:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL] We're grateful\Nfor this food.
Dialogue: 99,0:15:41.62,0:15:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO] Mm...
Dialogue: 99,0:15:42.83,0:15:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so good.
Dialogue: 99,0:15:44.25,0:15:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It is, isn't it?
Dialogue: 99,0:15:45.79,0:15:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And we bake it ourselves.
Dialogue: 99,0:15:47.75,0:15:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Master's an excellent chef.
Dialogue: 99,0:15:49.63,0:15:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He is!
Dialogue: 99,0:15:51.09,0:15:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the locally grown wheat\Nthat makes the difference.
Dialogue: 99,0:15:58.06,0:16:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco exclaims softly]
Dialogue: 99,0:16:00.64,0:16:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[exclaims]
Dialogue: 99,0:16:02.81,0:16:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This area's vegetables\Nare of superior quality as well.
Dialogue: 99,0:16:06.15,0:16:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- [COCO] Thanks! Delicious!\N- Thank you, Master Qifrey!
Dialogue: 99,0:16:08.65,0:16:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,♪
Dialogue: 99,0:16:33.55,0:16:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO] Mom... [sniffles]
Dialogue: 99,0:16:42.39,0:16:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[birds chirping]
Dialogue: 99,0:16:44.31,0:16:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO] So I need\Nto take tests of some kind
Dialogue: 99,0:16:46.52,0:16:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to become\Nan apprentice.
Dialogue: 99,0:16:49.15,0:16:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But it sure would be nice\Nto get some specifics
Dialogue: 99,0:16:51.86,0:16:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,on what exactly it is\NI have to do.
Dialogue: 99,0:16:54.20,0:16:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[QIFREY]\NDo about what, exactly?
Dialogue: 99,0:16:55.91,0:16:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco gasps]
Dialogue: 99,0:16:58.37,0:17:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a great deal about magic\Nyou won't find in any book.
Dialogue: 99,0:17:01.83,0:17:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust me, it's best to learn\Nby doing. So here.
Dialogue: 99,0:17:05.25,0:17:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they?
Dialogue: 99,0:17:06.92,0:17:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Your components,
Dialogue: 99,0:17:08.50,0:17:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,tools for drawing magic.
Dialogue: 99,0:17:11.63,0:17:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow!
Dialogue: 99,0:17:13.72,0:17:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 99,0:17:16.93,0:17:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 99,0:17:18.55,0:17:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A pen, just like the wand.
Dialogue: 99,0:17:21.89,0:17:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It still scares me to hold this.
Dialogue: 99,0:17:24.48,0:17:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But no...
Dialogue: 99,0:17:26.31,0:17:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, I'm going to save you\Nno matter what!
Dialogue: 99,0:17:29.73,0:17:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Master Qifrey,\NI'm ready to learn!
Dialogue: 99,0:17:32.78,0:17:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, let's begin.
Dialogue: 99,0:17:41.95,0:17:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[QIFREY]\NAre you all right, Coco?
Dialogue: 99,0:17:43.75,0:17:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we take a break?
Dialogue: 99,0:17:46.21,0:17:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO] No. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 99,0:17:49.29,0:17:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 99,0:17:50.75,0:17:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you sum up\Nall that you've learned so far?
Dialogue: 99,0:17:52.92,0:17:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 99,0:17:55.13,0:17:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, to start with,
Dialogue: 99,0:17:57.30,0:17:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,a spell is composed\Nof three elements.
Dialogue: 99,0:18:00.14,0:18:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The sigil lies in the center.
Dialogue: 99,0:18:02.60,0:18:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's surrounded by\Nmarkings called signs.
Dialogue: 99,0:18:05.64,0:18:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, the outer circle\Nthat completes it,
Dialogue: 99,0:18:08.77,0:18:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,that's called the ring.
Dialogue: 99,0:18:10.27,0:18:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The types of sigil are Fire,
Dialogue: 99,0:18:13.07,0:18:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Water,
Dialogue: 99,0:18:14.94,0:18:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Light,
Dialogue: 99,0:18:16.45,0:18:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and Wind.
Dialogue: 99,0:18:18.20,0:18:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They determine\Nwhat kind of magic it is.
Dialogue: 99,0:18:21.49,0:18:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The signs determine what form\Nthe magic ultimately takes,
Dialogue: 99,0:18:25.54,0:18:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,as well as its size\Nand direction.
Dialogue: 99,0:18:29.79,0:18:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Lastly, when the outer ring\Nis completed,
Dialogue: 99,0:18:33.21,0:18:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that locks the seal in place\Nand activates the spell.
Dialogue: 99,0:18:36.80,0:18:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Memorizing all this is\Nreally taking it out of me.
Dialogue: 99,0:18:39.43,0:18:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But you explained it,\Nthat's what counts!
Dialogue: 99,0:18:43.10,0:18:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. I'm going to try\Ndrawing one now!
Dialogue: 99,0:18:45.85,0:18:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for you! That's the spirit!
Dialogue: 99,0:18:50.81,0:18:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco sighs]
Dialogue: 99,0:18:53.98,0:18:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco sighs]
Dialogue: 99,0:18:56.86,0:18:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco exclaims softly]
Dialogue: 99,0:19:01.24,0:19:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[QIFREY] Uh?
Dialogue: 99,0:19:02.49,0:19:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Coco grunts]\N- [Qifrey gasps]
Dialogue: 99,0:19:04.12,0:19:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- [QIFREY] Don't throw it away.\N- [gasps]
Dialogue: 99,0:19:06.12,0:19:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Please don't look!
Dialogue: 99,0:19:08.83,0:19:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not even worthy\Nof your attention!
Dialogue: 99,0:19:11.29,0:19:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sloppy,
Dialogue: 99,0:19:12.83,0:19:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and the lines are all wobbly,\Nand it's a great big mess.
Dialogue: 99,0:19:15.34,0:19:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it is.
Dialogue: 99,0:19:17.21,0:19:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're only just learning.
Dialogue: 99,0:19:19.01,0:19:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,To that end, here's something\Nyou may want to look at.
Dialogue: 99,0:19:22.84,0:19:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,See this spot?\NYour ring doesn't fully connect.
Dialogue: 99,0:19:25.56,0:19:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless the circle is complete,\Nthe spell won't activate.
Dialogue: 99,0:19:28.85,0:19:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO] Oh.
Dialogue: 99,0:19:32.06,0:19:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[QIFREY]\NIt's natural to be unsteady
Dialogue: 99,0:19:34.02,0:19:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,when you're getting used\Nto something new.
Dialogue: 99,0:19:35.77,0:19:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're like a foal\Nthat's just learning to stand.
Dialogue: 99,0:19:38.53,0:19:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry.
Dialogue: 99,0:19:40.15,0:19:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be running wild\Nin no time at all.
Dialogue: 99,0:19:44.24,0:19:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, connect the lines,\Nand activate the spell.
Dialogue: 99,0:20:00.88,0:20:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Coco screams]\N- [Qifrey gasps]
Dialogue: 99,0:20:02.09,0:20:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I am so sorry!
Dialogue: 99,0:20:03.39,0:20:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an accident!\NI didn't mean to!
Dialogue: 99,0:20:06.35,0:20:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco screams]
Dialogue: 99,0:20:08.06,0:20:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO] I am\Nso, so, so, so sorry.
Dialogue: 99,0:20:09.89,0:20:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me dry it off. [pants]
Dialogue: 99,0:20:12.77,0:20:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is it working?\N- [QIFREY] Settle down, Coco!
Dialogue: 99,0:20:14.52,0:20:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Apologies, Agott.
Dialogue: 99,0:20:15.69,0:20:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- Are you all right?\N- [COCO] Better?
Dialogue: 99,0:20:18.61,0:20:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfectly fine.
Dialogue: 99,0:20:20.32,0:20:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really not bothered\Nin the least.
Dialogue: 99,0:20:23.36,0:20:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But may I ask for a look\Nat the casting seal she drew?
Dialogue: 99,0:20:26.37,0:20:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[QIFREY] Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 99,0:20:29.41,0:20:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[AGOTT] Ah, here's the problem.
Dialogue: 99,0:20:31.50,0:20:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco exclaims softly]
Dialogue: 99,0:20:36.21,0:20:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[AGOTT] Look...
Dialogue: 99,0:20:37.50,0:20:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This sign is longer\Nthan the others.
Dialogue: 99,0:20:40.42,0:20:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It amplified the pressure\Nin this direction,
Dialogue: 99,0:20:43.13,0:20:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,causing the water\Nto come gushing out.
Dialogue: 99,0:20:45.68,0:20:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[QIFREY] Well done!\NAstutely observed, as always.
Dialogue: 99,0:20:49.51,0:20:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[Qifrey sighs]
Dialogue: 99,0:20:51.22,0:20:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, she should be in\Nvery good hands with you.
Dialogue: 99,0:20:53.52,0:20:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO] Huh?
Dialogue: 99,0:20:59.73,0:21:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,For the next few days,
Dialogue: 99,0:21:01.49,0:21:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be away\Nvisiting the Great Hall.
Dialogue: 99,0:21:04.11,0:21:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,While I'm gone,
Dialogue: 99,0:21:05.11,0:21:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,do look after her,\Nwon't you, Agott?
Dialogue: 99,0:21:07.49,0:21:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I will. Of course.
Dialogue: 99,0:21:09.45,0:21:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[door opens]
Dialogue: 99,0:21:10.87,0:21:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Hold on!
Dialogue: 99,0:21:12.12,0:21:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,One may learn much indeed\Nfrom their peers.
Dialogue: 99,0:21:14.71,0:21:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll see. Watch her closely\Nand take it all in.
Dialogue: 99,0:21:17.54,0:21:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[Coco gasps]
Dialogue: 99,0:21:19.09,0:21:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Master, I...
Dialogue: 99,0:21:21.88,0:21:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[door closes]
Dialogue: 99,0:21:25.47,0:21:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I am sorry\Nabout before. I never--
Dialogue: 99,0:21:28.26,0:21:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I said I wasn't bothered,\Ndidn't I?
Dialogue: 99,0:21:30.51,0:21:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can stop apologizing.
Dialogue: 99,0:21:33.77,0:21:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- More importantly...\N- [gasps]
Dialogue: 99,0:21:36.10,0:21:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to prove yourself,
Dialogue: 99,0:21:38.52,0:21:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and I intend to make you.
Dialogue: 99,0:21:40.32,0:21:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,As of now,
Dialogue: 99,0:21:41.36,0:21:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the cushy little lessons\Nare over.
Dialogue: 99,0:21:43.61,0:21:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And your test has begun.
Dialogue: 99,0:21:47.28,0:21:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[COCO] What...
Dialogue: 99,0:21:52.49,0:21:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,♪
Dialogue: 99,0:22:06.05,0:22:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[♪ closing theme song playing]
